data.description: ***PAID-OFF SOLAR PANELS***This beautiful, single-story home has plenty of upgrades to offer. Subject property offers 3 ample bedrooms plus a den/office, and 2 full bathrooms. As you make your way inside the property you will come across new interior paint, new flooring, and a remodeled kitchen with new ceiling light fixtures. The bathrooms were also recently renovated, and new vanities were installed. Best part of all, this wonderful home will have paid-off solar panels, so one less utility bill for you, and your family to worry about. This home sweet home is centrally located minutes away from Marie Kerr Park, Rancho Vista Golf course, shopping centers, restaurants, and easy access to the freeway, making this home commuter friendly.
